text: Saikhan-Ovoo may refer to: * Saikhan-Ovoo, Dundgovi, a sum (district) in central Mongolia * Saikhan-Ovoo, Bulgan, an urban-type settlement or village in northern Mongolia * Saikhan-Ovoo coal mine, an underground coal mine in northern Mongolia ==See also== * Saikhan (disambiguation)
title: Saikhan-Ovoo
